                "text": "As a standard action, a chitikin can rub its antennae together to emit a terrifying scream. Each creature within 50 feet must succeed at a DC 12 Will saving throw or become panicked for 2d4 rounds. Whether or not it succeeds at its save, the creature is immune to the chitikin\u2019s shriek for 24 hours. This is a sonic, mind-affecting, fear effect. The save DC is Charisma-based."
